<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>As noted on fw-mvc, the logic of Zend_Controller_Front::throwExceptions() is faulty, and should be rewritten to:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
public function throwExceptions($flag = null)
{
    if ($flag !== null) {
        $this-&gt;_throwExceptions = (boolean) $flag;
        return $this;
    }
    return $this-&gt;_throwExceptions;
}
</code></pre>

